Based on the Haxe programming language, making it cross-platform.
Ideal for 2D games, especially retro-style pixel art games.
Provides tools for physics, collisions, input, and more.
Open-source and has a large library of pre-made assets and modules.
Supports cross-platform development (HTML5, Windows, macOS, Android, iOS).
Lightweight, perfect for small teams and indie developers.

Website: https://haxeflixel.com
